Name: halotools
Version: 0.7
Summary: Package designed to analyze N-body simulations and constrain models of cosmology and galaxy evolution.
Home-page: http://astropy.org/
Author: Andrew Hearin
Author-email: ahearin@anl.gov
License: BSD
Description: 
        Halotools is a specialized python package
        for building and testing models of the galaxy-halo connection,
        and analyzing catalogs of dark matter halos.
        
